561
01:51:13,375 --> 01:51:15,377
I'm sorry. I must be in the wrong place.

562
01:51:15,460 --> 01:51:17,254
No, you're in the right place.

563
01:51:18,380 --> 01:51:19,882
You probably don't remember me.

564
01:51:19,965 --> 01:51:22,634
I did root canal on you
about five years ago.

565
01:51:23,177 --> 01:51:24,887
Jim Spalding referred you.

566
01:51:27,055 --> 01:51:28,599
Oh, yeah, yeah.

567
01:51:33,770 --> 01:51:35,522
I'm Kelly's husband.

568
01:51:37,357 --> 01:51:38,817
Jerry Lovett.

569
01:51:39,902 --> 01:51:41,153
Kelly wanted...

570
01:51:42,988 --> 01:51:44,781
Kelly wanted to be here...

571
01:51:47,451 --> 01:51:50,078
Look, this is very hard for everyone.

572
01:51:51,788 --> 01:51:54,791
